We're a family based business, so we work as a family, we work together to give you the best value for your time and money.
We offer to refinish or resurface your old bathtub so you don't have to spend a lot of time and money to replace it.
Why go with reglazing ?
1. Quality: your bathtub will look and feel like a new bathtub.
2. Time: Our trained staff can get your tub back to new in one to days only.
3. Economy: our service will cost you a fraction of what replacing the tub will.
4. Peace of mind: we offer a three years warranty on all our services.
services:
Cast Iron bathtub and sink Reglazing.
Fiberglass bathtub and sink Reglazing.
Vinyl bathtub and sink Reglazing.
backsplash Reglazing.
Tiles Reglazing.
